56
00:03:26,005 --> 00:03:27,802
Sorry, was I blunt?

57
00:03:27,941 --> 00:03:29,169
Too blunt.

58
00:03:29,375 --> 00:03:31,843
But hey, this is how I
get when I see people...

59
00:03:31,911 --> 00:03:34,971
...who could do better or
who kinda miss the mark.

60
00:03:38,618 --> 00:03:39,346
Hi!

61
00:03:39,619 --> 00:03:40,608
Sorry.

62
00:03:40,687 --> 00:03:42,814
This is just how Saki is.

63
00:03:45,825 --> 00:03:49,784
