I Am from the Planet Otaku

64
00:03:54,667 --> 00:03:58,899
Like I said, those friends were
mundanes! I was being considerate.

65
00:03:58,972 --> 00:04:00,371
That's a lie.

66
00:04:00,607 --> 00:04:02,008
Ogiue was there too.

67
00:04:02,008 --> 00:04:04,738
