193
00:12:07,126 --> 00:12:07,751
You call that a fight!
Huh?

194
00:12:07,893 --> 00:12:11,954
"Weren't we having a fight?"
Talk about overly self-conscious!

195
00:12:13,099 --> 00:12:15,124
That's so otaku!

196
00:12:16,168 --> 00:12:17,863
Okay, I get it now.

197
00:12:19,138 --> 00:12:21,129
So, want to get some food?

198
00:12:21,407 --> 00:12:23,705
Huh? Wh-why?

199
00:12:24,043 --> 00:12:27,444
To "make up," of course.
I'm hungry, anyway.

200
00:12:27,947 --> 00:12:32,111
Or will you say something otaku like, "I can't eat
with a friend's girlfriend."

201
00:12:32,184 --> 00:12:35,085
Kaiten Sushigen

202
